  "detailed_description": "FLATLAND - Vol. 1 is a fast-paced hardcore platformer featuring hand-crafted levels and Lightning-fast respawns. Help Square survive his journey to the depths of Flatland, a minimalist neon-style 2D world. Run, jump, die, learn, repeat.<br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Controls are simple and accessible but with several layers of depth to master<br></li><li> Ramping up in difficulty from not-so-easy to soul crushing, FLATLAND - Vol 1 features hand-crafted levels with increasing challenges and secrets to uncover.<br></li><li> Lightning-fast respawns keep you in the flow even in more difficult levels<br></li><li> Challenging, fast and fun gameplay.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "FLATLAND - Vol. 1 is a fast-paced hardcore platformer featuring hand-crafted levels and Lightning-fast respawns. Help Square survive his journey to the depths of Flatland, a minimalist neon-style 2D world. Run, jump, die, learn, repeat.<br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Controls are simple and accessible but with several layers of depth to master<br></li><li> Ramping up in difficulty from not-so-easy to soul crushing, FLATLAND - Vol 1 features hand-crafted levels with increasing challenges and secrets to uncover.<br></li><li> Lightning-fast respawns keep you in the flow even in more difficult levels<br></li><li> Challenging, fast and fun gameplay.</li></ul>",
